{"word":"G5591 - ψυχικός - psychikós - psoo-khee-kos' - Natural","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ψυχικός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">psychikós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">psoo-khee-kos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Natural</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஜென்ம சுபாவமான, ஜென்ம - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"the sensuous nature with its subjection to appetite and passion"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5590 - ψυχή - psychḗ - psoo-khay'/5590\">G5590</a>; <i>sensitive</i> that is, <i>animate</i> (in distinction on the one hand from <a href=\"#/G4152 - πνευματικός - pneumatikós - pnyoo-mat-ik-os'/4152\">G4152</a>, which is the higher or <i>renovated</i> nature; and on the other from <a href=\"#/G5446 - φυσικός - physikós - foo-see-kos'/5446\">G5446</a>, which is the lower or <i>bestial</i> nature): - natural, sensual.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1374/1374\">G1374</a>, <a href=\"#/G3642/3642\">G3642</a>, <a href=\"#/G403/403\">G403</a>, <a href=\"#/G404/404\">G404</a>, <a href=\"#/G5590/5590\">G5590</a>, <a href=\"#/G5591/5591\">G5591</a>"}]}